Constructor for the S4 associations object.

associations.Rd

Constructor for the S4 associations object.

Usage

associations(
  associations = associations_tbl(),
  loci = loci_tbl(),
  risk_alleles = risk_alleles_tbl(),
  genes = reported_genes_tbl(),
  ensembl_ids = ensembl_ids_tbl(),
  entrez_ids = entrez_ids_tbl()
)

Arguments

associations

An associations_tbl tibble.

loci

A loci_tbl tibble.

risk_alleles

A risk_alleles_tbl tibble.

genes

A reported_genes_tbl tibble.

ensembl_ids

A ensembl_ids_tbl tibble.

entrez_ids

A entrez_ids_tbl tibble.

Value

An object of class associations.
